commands.name: Disable Unused Events Bundle

commands.name: Disable Unused Events Blocks
commands.command: drush dis cu_events_calendar_block -y; sudo -u apache drush pmu cu_events_calendar_block -y

commands.name: DRUSH - Add forms bundle to site.
TEMP - Disabling Webform Bundle and modules
commands.command: drush dis cu_forms_bundle cu_webform webform cu_feedback recaptcha captcha captcha_webform -y; sudo -u apache drush pmu cu_forms_bundle -y

commands.name: TEMP - Uninstall Form Bundle Dependencies
commands.command: drush pmu cu_webform recaptcha -y; sudo -u apache drush pmu webform -y; sudo -u apache drush pmu captcha_webform -y; sudo -u apache drush pmu cu_feedback captcha -y
